  <brief_title>Topical Henna Preparation for the Treatment of Hand Foot Skin Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Controlled Open-label Trial of a Topical Henna Preparation for the Treatment of Hand-Foot Skin Syndrome and Its Associated Symptoms</official_title>
