  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether henna paste is effective in the treatment
      of hand-foot skin syndrome, induced by the drugs Capecitabine and pegylated liposomal
      doxorubicin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
